1. *Bit* ću na put za Beograd za vikend (I will go on a trip to Belgrade this weekend).
2. Ona je *bila* u pravu (She was right).
3. Možemo pokušati da *budemo* iskreni (We can try to be honest).
4. *Biti* tamo je bilo potpuno različito (To be there was completely different).
5. Oni su *bića* koja vole da se igraju (They are beings that love to play).